OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a mostly dry start, the
OL,6,Fday will see bight spells interspersed
OL,7,Fwith blustery showers. These mainly in
OL,8,Fthe west and the south. Strong south
OL,9,Fto southwest winds may reach gale
OL,10,Fforce at times.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThe showers will clear from
OL,13,Fthe evening to leave the night dry
OL,14,Fwith increasing clear periods. This
OL,15,Ftogether with the wind falling light
OL,16,Fwill bring a patchy inland frost.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FThe morning will be mostly dry
OL,19,Fwith bright spells. Cloud and
OL,20,Fscattered showers spread northeast
OL,21,Fduring the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
